BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 52 594 Tm (- Collects seven outbreak parameters in a browser form.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 52 581 Tm (- Returns ML-predicted peak infected population, outbreak duration, and total infected population.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 52 568 Tm (- Exposes a JSON /predict API for programmatic predictions.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 52 555 Tm (- Exposes a JSON /simulate API that returns SIR timelines and optional agent snapshots.) Tj ET
